{"tid":520200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【16歲女做CEO】 「我賺成百萬 你哋仲係基本工資」","createTime":"2018-01-05T07:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T11:29:47.000Z","uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e184875bc6db5af918d6f347f9db71289ccb2cbd","tid":520200,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T07:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/152556_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F152556_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=113eb8f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「在我拿幾十萬、上百萬的投資和獎金的時候，很多成年人還在打着《王者榮耀》，拿着基本工資，過着十年如一日生活&hellip;&hellip;」近日，來自廣東16歲的00後CEO喻言，在湖南芒果TV節目《放學別走》中瘋狂吐槽成年人，不僅引起主持人驚訝、汗顏，更引起網民熱議。<br />\n<br />\n「大家好，我是喻言，今年16歲，我也是『諾亞大陸』的聯合創始人，以及現任CEO。」「很多人會質疑公司的真實性，甚至懷疑我們是那個融資節目找來的托（台下出現一陣笑聲），最根本原因我是00後。」一身紅裙打扮的喻言從滿自信地說：「其實我覺得僅僅因為年紀輕，所以就認為下孩子創業，是不知天高地厚，是胡鬧的話，是完全講不通邏輯的，因為我認為有很多大人，他們在創業的時候，也會衝動行事，也會耍小孩子脾氣，在我拿幾十萬上百萬的投資和獎金的時候，很多成年人還在打着《王者榮耀》，拿着基本工資，過着十年如一日生活&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n2015年6月，以鍛煉的心態參加科技部「中國創新創業大賽」的喻言，出乎意料地獲得了互聯網團隊廣東省第一，國家獎勵50萬元人民幣（約60萬港元）創新大獎，因此走上了創業之路。她獲得融資的項目叫「諾亞大陸」，其實要做的也非常簡單，就是建造一個基於人脈關係的分享網購平台，將網購從目前的「物以類聚」，升級為「人以群分」，人們通過熟人來找尋物品，相當於人為商品代言，諾亞大陸為交易擔保，從而讓網購變得簡單、放心，也解決網購欺詐和假冒偽劣問題。<br />\n<br />\n「所以你的公司，我剛才沒聽明白，相當把馬雲和馬化騰兩家一網打盡？」「對，其實......」喻言斬釘截鐵的言論，把主持人撒貝寧嚇到彈起。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180105/57664060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180105%2F57664060&d=5eF4tT49bOmdx1L6XUUpv0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=750b6dba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180105%2F57664060&h=d2a4cc60\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180105/57664060</a>"},{"pid":"3fa6238974dcbd1a7d904d69ccff9dfcbc73f09a","tid":520200,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T07:39:50.000Z","msg":"好威威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70e218af0c211f956f96745017b5b74c48b6e21","tid":520200,"uid":41508,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T07:40:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c35a28d5c87b1fa35565f12554b9a4b90f051c20","tid":520200,"uid":5521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T07:53:51.000Z","msg":"冇人識你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人起朵你起朵<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2ff75b8fb249f56ba6adec40517626a1fff8d6","tid":520200,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T07:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd9c2e6839acc1055fc7fd679e2a498b4c916e6","tid":520200,"uid":99745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:14:36.000Z","msg":"咁人地真係串得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35b96b657ce5fe8aa70d0920525dd566e720219","tid":520200,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"787d82ffda2f689a8d9b2b0cdeac36194ad2ed9d","tid":520200,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b35b96b657ce5fe8aa70d0920525dd566e720219","tid":520200,"uid":57705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4fd9c2e6839acc1055fc7fd679e2a498b4c916e6","tid":520200,"uid":99745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:14:36.000Z","msg":"咁人地真係串得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T11:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6387d7b36ebb47b6cf649abd728bf5514dcd4282","tid":520200,"